<p>I'm keeping both this page and the original downvoted for the following reasons:</p>
<ol>
<li><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/forum/t-144376/deleted:agent-nekochris-personnel-file#post-470147">What Yoric says here on the old page's discussion thread.</a> Not <em>quite</em> enough for a downvote in and of itself <em>if done well</em>, but a total votekill in conjunction with …</li>
<li>Reading more like the Circumstances of Recovery section of an SCP entry for the electrical elemental than like an introduction to the Agent NekoChris character as a person. If there are any standard guidelines for personnel pages, I don't know about them, but I'm pretty sure they're meant more to introduce your character's personality, quirks, skills, and role and to list your contributions, not to add something that would be better handled in an SCP entry or Foundation Tale. And speaking of adding…</li>
<li>Creating a new page instead of just fixing the old one.</li>
</ol>

