														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-509417">
									

<p>That's fine. I'm ignoring downvotes from this point forward. I don't think they should apply to member profiles. Maybe you haven't exactly read through the multitude of profiles available so far. Let me point a few out.</p>
<p>One has a Poke`mon Trainer.</p>
<p>One has someone who has a dog for a head.</p>
<p>One has someone who has a spider for a head.</p>
<p>One has what appears to be a viking warrior.</p>
<p>One has a spoon.</p>
<p>Given that there is a generally absurd nature to some profiles listed here it angers the piss out of me the level of scrutiny given to what I've written on mine. Especially when it comes from people who don't even have one of their own.</p>
<p>That said, I've been focusing on getting the symbiote creature's entry perfected before I come back and revisit this. From my viewpoint however, it reads as what could be a legitimate file pulled from HR for review. More so than some others.</p>

							</div>

								
					
