<p>Neko,</p>
<p>In the end, what appears to be the issue is the heavy involvement of your electrical being in your character profile. if you can reduce it's mention to a single paragraph or sentence, i think you will find the approval of your page rises in direct proportion to the amount you reduce the SCP mention.</p>
<p>It's too focused on the interplay between the item and the Agent. Do up the whole page with zero mention of the SCP…then add it at the very end, almost like an aside.</p>
<p>However, i have to agree with Fish: this isn't enough of a issue to warrant the building conversation. if it's bad, we will let you know. if it's REALLY bad, we'll ask you to change it. You will or will not do so, which will elicit the appropriate response. Let's all try and move forward now.</p>

